<h1>Why Should You learn Code?</h1>
<h3>By: Devin Casper</h3>
<body>
<p>
Coding is the most popular need for big buisnesses and companies. Many companies need people to design websites and programs, like applications, operating sytems, and many more.  
</p>
<p>
Many online games use code that is not too complex. Many of them use elements that are used in websites.
</p>
</body>
<a href="https://codecombat.com">Code Combat</a>

is a website that has you code to win a battle. It is a more simple version of coding. This is for children and people who want to learn in their extra time.
</p>

If you would like to learn the more barebones types of coding, you can vist one like 
<a href="https://www.codecademy.com/">Code Academy</a>
or
<a href="https://www.khanacademy.org/">Khan Academy.</a>
These websites will teach the coding that is used for today's websites and games. It will teach you the elements of HTML and many other elements of coding.
<p>
After learning code, you can create many things. For example:
<p>
